unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(BOSS_INTRO, ID_BOSS)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_GUILTY) then
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(ID_GUILTY, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
		Hydra.ActorSetAIState(ID_GUILTY, "aggressive")
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(ID_EFFIGY, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(ID_BOSS, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(ID_EFFIGY, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(ID_BOSS, true)
	
	local House3Actors = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "House3")
	
	for i, idActor in pairs(House3Actors) do
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idActor, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActor, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetAIState(idActor, "aggressive")
	end
end

unk_9c63f9d.value:
Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_OPEN_DOOR)
Hydra.ActorDisable(ID_SWITCH_DOOR)

for i, idActor in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "House3")) do
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idActor)
end
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(ID_EFFIGY, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(ID_BOSS, false)

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_GUILTY) then
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_GUILTY, ANIMSET_PRAYER)
	Hydra.ActorSetUseAlternateName(ID_GUILTY, true) --Switches npc to alternate name
end

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_GUILTY) then
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_CRAZED, ANIMSET_PRAYER)
	Hydra.ActorSetUseAlternateName(ID_CRAZED, true)
end
